IMAPAccount sculch
Host mail.runbox.com
User mario%scul.ch
PassCmd "gpg --quiet --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.mutt/.sculch.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore sculch-remote
Account sculch

MaildirStore sculch-local
Path ~/.mail/mario@scul.ch/
Inbox ~/.mail/mario@scul.ch/Inbox

Channel sculch-inbox
Master :sculch-remote:
Slave :sculch-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel sculch-sent
Master :sculch-remote:Sent
Slave :sculch-local:Sent
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel sculch-drafts
Master :sculch-remote:Drafts
Slave :sculch-local:Drafts
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel sculch-spam
Master :sculch-remote:Spam
Slave :sculch-local:Spam
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel sculch-trash
Master :sculch-remote:Trash
Slave :sculch-local:Trash
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Group sculch
Channel sculch-inbox
Channel sculch-sent
Channel sculch-drafts
Channel sculch-spam
Channel sculch-trash

